{"tid":1745344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依條垃圾Ragazine主持屈鳩鄭文傑叫雞","createTime":"2019-11-22T07:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:18.000Z","uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67ffdec607e5904da2e47677072e1724f4d2b79c","tid":1745344,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"人地明明已經講到明唔會做任何對不起自己珍惜同愛嘅人嘅, 轉頭條仆街話&quot;咁即係有啦&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後仲要講咗幾次!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wPwxyr0o0Lo?t=1011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwPwxyr0o0Lo%3Ft%3D1011&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=445a6ed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wPwxyr0o0Lo?t=1011</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋蘋果都已經搵到個場其實係普通骨場囉!<br />\n【抗暴之戰】鄭文傑「嫖妓」按摩店曝光 老牌骨場多港人幫襯<br />\n英國駐香港總領事館前僱員鄭文傑（Simon Cheng）今年8月到內地出差時，因嫖妓被捕及拘留15天。事隔3個月後，鄭向英美傳媒爆料，指自己因香港反修例示威活動，遭中國公安嚴刑拷問。內地官媒《人民日報》昨釋出鄭文傑出入按摩場所及「認罪」的影片，力證鄭被捕合乎法理，隨即引來關注。有網民指，涉事按摩場所是位於深圳羅湖區東門中路的「麗水雲間休閒會所」。麗水雲間是當地一間老牌按摩店，以往有不少港人惠顧。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191122/60295331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F60295331&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=5bd3d71a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F60295331&h=c83afb90\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191122/60295331</a>"},{"pid":"8ba00f539551bb310877894128110e3be92535a6","tid":1745344,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=f93926b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}